{"tid":2362001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"長者難抵嚴寒 兩日八人猝死","createTime":"2021-01-11T06:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T08:35:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4906ab02d0983805accb5a0ecb820dbe6bc252f8","tid":2362001,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/2RPIZ5K5E5FY7E752FH33X6L2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2F2RPIZ5K5E5FY7E752FH33X6L2A%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2Ba3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=737c2c6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2F2RPIZ5K5E5FY7E752FH33X6L2A%2F&h=d9d8ccf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/2RPIZ5K5E5FY7E752FH33X6L2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n長者難抵嚴寒 兩日八人猝死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JkuzC-LlZMU89Gr1xY7qJObjZy4=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BBGFIQGU3JE6LDOGH2L4CYBZCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJkuzC-LlZMU89Gr1xY7qJObjZy4%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBBGFIQGU3JE6LDOGH2L4CYBZCI.jpg&h=d0f53bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■心臟科醫生梁達智指溫度驟降易誘發心臟病、中風，長者務必注意保暖。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港持續多日寒冷，繼前日至少三名長者在寓所內暈倒猝死後，昨再多五名長者疑抵受不住寒冷天氣，先後暈倒死亡，其中一名老翁更疑是露宿者。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一人疑為露宿者<br />\n<br />\n昨凌晨零時許，有途人在鰂魚涌英皇道1048號街頭，發現一名老翁不適後報警，老翁送東區醫院後證實不治。事後警方未能在他身上找到身份證明文件，不排除是露宿人士。在相若時間，一名居於筲箕灣耀興道老人院的96歲葉姓婆婆，疑難抵寒冷，在院內不適暈倒，救護員到場時她已昏迷，送院搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n另外，下午1時許將軍澳善明邨善智樓一名92歲鄭姓老翁，在單位內昏迷送院後死亡；約3時許，沙田銀城街一間老人院一名90多歲婆婆突然不適，亦送院後死亡；秀茂坪邨秀逸樓一名88歲吳姓老翁，亦於差不多時間被發現在單位內不省人事，倒卧地上，保安員報警，救護員到場證實他已死亡。<br />\n<br />\n心臟科專科醫生梁達智指，溫度驟降容易誘發心臟病、中風，長者務必注意保暖，盡量留在室內。他又建議露宿人士到避寒中心，惟香港社區組織協會幹事吳衞東指，因露宿者憂離開露宿位置後，家當會被食環掃走；部份中心偏遠亦令使用量低。"},{"pid":"afcf5f489f77ff3e24d91991031cfb2ab47683af","tid":2362001,"uid":337986,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"啲廢老真係唔捱得<br />\n凍少少就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2ce47dfe37fa71655f96f7bb1e32b354cc59a7","tid":2362001,"uid":25560,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"afcf5f489f77ff3e24d91991031cfb2ab47683af","tid":2362001,"uid":337986,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"啲廢老真係唔捱得<br />\n凍少少就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"口德 -1"},{"pid":"2d139ee7f2c038a7a3b4a04b825087ab40d1ca7b","tid":2362001,"uid":58630,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:58:17.000Z","msg":"渣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ec7ffc29388616b228cd2ef5cfe6852a3f2064","tid":2362001,"uid":197985,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"afcf5f489f77ff3e24d91991031cfb2ab47683af","tid":2362001,"uid":337986,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:50:54.000Z","msg":"啲廢老真係唔捱得<br />\n凍少少就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T06:59:36.000Z","msg":"住得老人院，訓得係條街點會係廢佬？真正廢佬係有錢有樣有仔有女架"},{"pid":"fb8a22dd0cfe50ff1031e297b02bbd07357ce9e9","tid":2362001,"uid":41087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"勁過武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f9b9dc9e94aeaa93f41c6b936e7b36d3f0a371","tid":2362001,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb8a22dd0cfe50ff1031e297b02bbd07357ce9e9","tid":2362001,"uid":41087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"勁過武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT